short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension that helps to develop LaxarJS applications

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extends the developer tools with a tab for LaxarJS applications. This extension helps you to analyze your LaxarJS application. It displays application events, helps visualizing the structure of the current page and allows to browse log messages.
